  <body>
    <p>A variety of actions are available for XHTML documents that can be found in
        <uicontrol>XHTML</uicontrol> menu, toolbar, contextual menu, and the <xref
        keyref="glossentry_content-completion-assistant"><term>Content Completion
        Assistant</term></xref>.</p>
    <section id="toolbar-actions-section">
      <title>XHTML Toolbar Actions</title>
      <p>The following default actions are available on the XHTML toolbar when editing in
          <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode (by default, they are also available in the
          <uicontrol>XHTML</uicontrol> menu and some of them are in various submenus of the
        contextual menu):</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Bold16.gif" id="image_j4x_qrn_ps"
              />Bold</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Changes the style of the selected text to <i>bold</i> by surrounding it
              with the <xmlelement>b</xmlelement> tag. You can use this action on multiple non-contiguous
              selections.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Italic16.png" id="image_k4x_qrn_ps"
                />Italic</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Changes the style of the selected text to <i>italic</i> by surrounding it
              with <xmlelement>i</xmlelement> tag. You can use this action on multiple non-contiguous
              selections.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Underline16.gif" id="image_l4x_qrn_ps"
                />Underline</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Changes the style of the selected text to <i>underline</i> by surrounding
              it with <xmlelement>u</xmlelement> tag. You can use this action on multiple non-contiguous
              selections.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Link16.png" id="image_m4x_qrn_ps"
              />Link</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xmlelement>a</xmlelement> element with an <xmlatt>href</xmlatt> attribute at the
              cursor position. You can type the URL of the reference you want to insert or use the
              browsing actions in the <uicontrol><image href="../img/BrowseDrop.png"
                  id="image_n4x_qrn_ps"/>Browse</uicontrol> drop-down menu.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Image16.gif" id="image_p4x_qrn_ps"/>Insert
                Image</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a graphic object at the cursor position. This is done by inserting an
              <xmlelement>img</xmlelement> element regardless of the current context. The following
              graphical formats are supported: GIF, JPG, JPEG, BMP, PNG, SVG.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert-media">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/HeadingDrop.png" id="image_q4x_qrn_ps"
                />Headings</uicontrol> Drop-down Menu</dt>
            <dd>A drop-down menu that includes actions for inserting <xmlelement>h1</xmlelement>,
              <xmlelement>h2</xmlelement>, <xmlelement>h3</xmlelement>, <xmlelement>h4</xmlelement>, <xmlelement>h5</xmlelement>,
              <xmlelement>h6</xmlelement> elements.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert-para-dlentry">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert-mathml-dlentry">
