            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert-ol-dlentry">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/VariableList16.gif" id="image_r4x_qrn_ps"/>Insert a
                definition list at the cursor position</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a definition list (<xmlelement>dl</xmlelement> element) with one list item (a
              <xmlelement>dt</xmlelement> child element and a <xmlelement>dd</xmlelement> child element). You can
